headline: CoStar Group To Present at Stephens 27th Annual Investment Conference
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., November 17, 2025--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, analytics, and 3D digital twin technology in the property markets, will present at Stephens 27th Annual Investment Conference. CFO Chris Lown and Head of Investor Relations Rich Simonelli will participate in a fireside chat on Thursday, November 20, 2025, at 9:00 a.m. CT.
